        "level": 3,
        "content_html": "<p>Domain I tests product knowledge of life insurance and annuities: how different policy types work, what problems they solve, and how they compare. It includes traditional whole life, interest‑sensitive and variable/adjustable products, term life types and features, individual annuity structures, and combination/joint life designs. The emphasis is on conceptual understanding (structure, guarantees, risk, cash value, and taxation basics), not detailed state‑law procedures.</p>"
