        "content_html": "<ul>\n<li>entity[\"company\",\"Pearson VUE\",\"testing company\"] “Texas Insurance Content Outlines” (effective Dec 1, 2025) shows this domain as <strong>15%</strong> and explicitly lists key provisions (entire contract, insuring clause, free look, consideration, grace period, reinstatement, incontestability, misstatement of age and gender, exclusions). This is likely <strong>directly testable</strong> because it shapes what appears on the exam. citeturn48view0turn49view0turn49view1</li>\n</ul>"
