        "content_html": "<p>To pass this domain, focus on the following core pillars:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>The Power Center</strong>: The Commissioner is the appointed administrative leader who enforces the code, examines carriers every 5 years, and can levy $25,000 penalties or issue C\\&amp;D orders.  </li>\n<li><strong>The Licensing Lifecycle</strong>: Pass the exam (or get a 180-day temporary), get appointed within 30 days, maintain 24 hours of CE (3 ethics), and report address/criminal changes promptly.  </li>\n<li><strong>The Ethical Boundary</strong>: Avoid the \"Big Three\" marketing sins—Misrepresentation (lying about benefits), Defamation (lying about rivals), and Rebating (sharing commissions).  </li>\n<li><strong>The Protection System</strong>: Handle claims with 15/15/5 precision (Acknowledge/Decide/Pay) and understand that the Guaranty Association is a quiet $300k safety net for member insurer failures.</li>\n</ul>"
